          <label className="block text-gray-700 text-xl font-bold mb-3">
            ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏à‡∏≥‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏î‡∏î‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏≤‡∏´‡∏≤‡∏£ (Dietary Restrictions)
